``` json
"multi_match" : {
   "query" : "mastodon aragon",
   "fields" : [ "Artist", "Album" ],
    "type":"something_that_does_not_exists"
}
```

the `multi_match` query just defaults to `bool` instead of throwing an exception which it should.

